Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
i think it is a good and effective way for a young person to transition from home with family rules and guidelines to a first stage of adulthood and self governance. a campus dorm provides more structure than offg campus living provides as a new student adaptes to college life.